Package: node-bcryptjs
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, nodejs (>= 12)
Description: Optimized bcrypt in plain JavaScript with zero dependencies
 bcryptjs is an optimized bcrypt implementation in plain JavaScript
 with zero dependencies, compatible with the C++ bcrypt binding and
 the original bcrypt implementation. Includes TypeScript support.
